RichEditor__h3" dir="auto"><span data-lexical-text="true">Tips</span></h3><p class="RichEditor__paragraph" dir="auto"><br></p><ul class="RichEditor__ul" dir="auto"><li value="1" class="RichEditor__listItem"><b><span data-lexical-text="true">Test drive the car</span></b><span data-lexical-text="true"> before buying.</span></li><li value="2" class="RichEditor__listItem"><span data-lexical-text="true">Check the vehicle history.</span></li><li value="3" class="RichEditor__listItem"><span data-lexical-text="true">Compare different models online.</span></li><li value="4" class="RichEditor__listItem"><em><span data-lexical-text="true">Avoid cars with hidden damage.</span></em></li></ul><p class="RichEditor__paragraph" dir="auto"><br></p><h2 class="RichEditor__h2" dir="auto"><span data-lexical-text="true">Car Buying Checklist</span></h2><p class="RichEditor__paragraph" dir="auto"><br></p><ul class="RichEditor__ul RichEditor__checklist" dir="auto"><li role="checkbox" tabindex="-1" aria-checked="true" value="1" class="RichEditor__listItem RichEditor__listItemChecked"><span data-lexical-text="true">Set a budget</span></li><li role="checkbox" tabindex="-1" aria-checked="true" value="2" class="RichEditor__listItem RichEditor__listItemChecked"><span data-lexical-text="true">Research car models</span></li><li role="checkbox" tabindex="-1" aria-checked="false" value="3" class="RichEditor__listItem RichEditor__listItemUnchecked"><span data-lexical-text="true">Test drive the car</span></li><li role="checkbox" tabindex="-1" aria-checked="false" value="4" class="RichEditor__listItem RichEditor__listItemUnchecked"><span data-lexical-text="true">Inspect the vehicle history</span></li><li role="checkbox" tabindex="-1" aria-checked="false" value="5" class="RichEditor__listItem RichEditor__listItemUnchecked"><span data-lexical-text="true">Compare insurance prices</span></li></ul><p class="RichEditor__paragraph" dir="auto"><br></p><blockquote class="RichEditor__quote" dir="auto"><p class="Ri